These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, italian, thai, polish
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, dog, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the italian is on the left or right of the thai##3
4. the polish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the polish is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
7. the italian is somewhere between the dutch and the owner of the horse##7
8. the italian and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9
9. the thai and the owner of the cat have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch | italian | thai     | polish |
| Pet           | dog   | turtle     | horse | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, rock-climbing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is board-games and the person drinking milk have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
7. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | hot-chocolate    | fanta | milk    |
| Hobby      | woodworking | singing | rock-climbing      | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, soy-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: carrot, potato, zucchini, broccoli
1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5
2. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
7. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
8. the person drinking lemonade and the person eating potato have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | soy-milk   | 7up    | tea  |
| Food       | potato | broccoli | carrot | zucchini |

