.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, writer, police-officer, designer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, rock, salsa, metal
1. the fan dubstep is the writer##1
2. the fan rock is on the right of the fan salsa##1
3. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the writer##5
4. the fan metal is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
5. the fan rock is on the left of the paramedic##1
6. the designer and the fan metal have the same parity positions##9
7. the police-officer is on the left or right of the paramedic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | police-officer | paramedic  | writer |
| Music-Genre   | salsa             | rock          | metal | dubstep    |

