.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, folk, gospel
4 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, rabbit, lizard
1. the fan folk is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the rat and the fan house have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the mouse and the fan indie have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the fan gospel##1
6. the fan indie is not the owner of the mouse##6
7. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
8. the owner of the rat is on the right of the fan house##1
9. the owner of the lizard is not the fan gospel##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | house | folk | gospel  | indie |
| Pet           | mouse   | rat     | rabbit | lizard      |

