.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, satire, horror, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, argentine, chinese
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
4. the dutch and the person watching horror movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching time-travel movies and the dutch have different parity positions##9
6. the argentine is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
8. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the chinese##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | romance | horror | time-travel |
| Nationality   | chinese        | argentine    | dutch   | indonesian |

