The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, snowboarding, swimming
1. the fan r&b is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
2. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is swimming and the fan disco have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the fan disco is not to the right of the fan techno##8
6. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan techno##5
7. the fan disco is somewhere to the right of the fan pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | r&b | disco         | techno     |
| Sport         | tennis | swimming  | snowboarding | biathlon |

