.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, rock-climbing, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, ferret, goat
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is not the owner of the goldfish##6
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the owner of the goat have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | photography | card-games | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | guinea-pig     | ferret     | goat     | goldfish    |

