.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, apple, lettuce, shiprot
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, boat, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is not to the left of the person eating orange##8
2. the person eating shiprot and the person driving the helicopter have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person eating apple is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person driving the helicopter##7
6. the person eating shiprot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | lettuce | orange   | apple | shiprot |
| Transport   | boat   | train | ship    | helicopter      |

