2. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is the person eating mango##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting and the person eating orange have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | mango | cabbage | tomato   | orange   |
| Hobby   | photography  | hiking   | collecting | fishing |

