.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, carrot, cabbage, pepper
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, british, pakistani, brazilian
1. the person eating pepper is not the brazilian##6
2. the brazilian is not to the right of the mexican##8
3. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person eating pepper##8
4. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
5. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
6. the brazilian is on the far left##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
8. the person eating papaya is the british##1
9. the person eating pepper and the mexican have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | carrot   | pepper    | cabbage | papaya    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | mexican | pakistani   | british |

