2. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
8. the person watching zombie movies and the person drinking milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching epic movies and the person drinking 7up have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice   | cola  | 7up  | milk |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | epic | drama | zombie      |

