.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, sprite, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b, country, rock
 1. the person drinking water and the fan country have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 3. the fan hip-hop is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking fanta##7
 4. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan country is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
 7. the person drinking tea and the fan d&b have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
 9. the fan rock is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the fan hip-hop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | tea | sprite  | water |
| Music-Genre   | rock | country     | hip-hop | d&b     |

