.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, collecting, sudoku
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 6. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 7. the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is hiking have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 9. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is hiking have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | lemonade        | milk   | hot-chocolate      |
| Hobby      | sudoku | collecting | hiking | filmmaking |

 